Title: Old Friends
Description:
Alright then, grab onto the ladder. We gotta get outa here!

We'll make a flyby of the town, and then I'm gonna get you to some old friends!
ObjectivesText: Speak with Thrall at the Warchief's Lookout on the Lost Isles.
RewardText:
I told you we would meet again, $n.

<The Warchief gives you an appraising look.>

Unfortunate that it's under such dire circumstances.
